             <div class="ir-receipt-commentary mobile-only">
                <h4>THE VERDICT</h4>
                <p>To eat this specific meal <em>tonight</em> by cooking it yourself, you have to spend nearly <strong>$29.00</strong> at the store.</p>
                <p>Sure, you have "leftovers." But now you are stuck eating the same thing. You have to eat Chili Mac for three days straight just to use up ingredients before they go bad.</p>
