      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ir-section ir-white-bg">
    <div class="ir-container ir-grid-50-50">
      <div class="ir-content-col">
        <h3>GUESSING VS. KNOWING</h3>
        <p>Trying to hit exact macros at home is hard. "Eyeballing" olive oil or cheese can add 200 calories to your meal without you noticing.</p>
        <p>Getting 59g of protein exactly right requires a food scale and math every single time you cook. We do the math for you in a lab. You just eat.</p>
        <p>Your most valuable asset is time. Stop trading your time for groceries.</p>
